statements.sql: select `v_projet_form`.*, `customers`.`customerName` from `v_projet_form` inner join `customers` on `v_projet_form`.`idCfp` = `customers`.`idCustomer` where `idFormateur` = 22 and `headYear` = '2025' order by `dateDebut` asc
select `v_union_projets`.* from `v_union_projets` where `idProjet` in (165) and project_status COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci = 'Terminé'

select `eval_chauds`.*, `type_questions`.`idTypeQuestion` from `eval_chauds` inner join `questions` on `eval_chauds`.`idQuestion` = `questions`.`idQuestion` inner join `type_questions` on `questions`.`idTypeQuestion` = `type_questions`.`idTypeQuestion` where `idProjet` in (165) and `type_questions`.`idTypeQuestion` = 2

select FORMAT(SUM(TIME_TO_SEC(intervalle_raw)) / 3600, 2) AS sumHourSession from `v_seances` inner join `v_union_projets` on `v_seances`.`idProjet` = `v_union_projets`.`idProjet` where `v_seances`.`idProjet` in (165) and v_union_projets.project_status COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci = 'Terminé' limit 1
